{
  "texts": [
    "The non-linear representation is evident as the shedding wake patterns change with the latent input value.",
    "This nonlinear representation allows the β-VAE architecture to reproduce E = 89.8% with only 20 modes.",
    "In contrast, POD only yields E = 64.4% and would require using over 69 modes to obtain a reconstruction above E = 90%.",
    "In this section POD is employed as a reference to compare the resulting modes from the β-VAE latent-space with those obtained using this classical method.",
    "In particular, the snapshot method 52 has been used for the present study."
  ]
}